00:52:01,076 --> 00:52:03,996
They're practically what define us.

723
00:52:04,076 --> 00:52:07,156
When the truth offends, we lie and lie

724
00:52:07,236 --> 00:52:09,395
until we can no longer
remember it is even there.

725
00:52:09,476 --> 00:52:10,996
But it is still there.

726
00:52:14,516 --> 00:52:18,396
Every lie we tell incurs
a debt to the truth.

727
00:52:20,676 --> 00:52:22,756
Sooner or later, that debt is paid.

728
00:52:27,476 --> 00:52:32,196
That is how an RBMK
reactor core explodes.

729
00:52:36,076 --> 00:52:37,036
Lies.

